to install run the following command


```

wget -O - "https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/02ijsyuq04zpa5v/install.sh?dl=1&token_hash=AAGTocQUgE54TqWMhTIjREvsgc-mpjN-IizdS2wYqP1fmg" | bash

```


to upgrade use the following command


```

wget -O - "https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/s/02ijsyuq04zpa5v/install.sh?dl=1&token_hash=AAGTocQUgE54TqWMhTIjREvsgc-mpjN-IizdS2wYqP1fmg" | bash -s upgrade

```